---
title: Cheese and Chicken Breast Spinach Penne Bake with Bacon Crumb
description: This Cheese and Chicken Breast Spinach Penne Bake is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
